---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import DemoBlock from '../components/DemoBlock.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Free Alpine.js UI Patterns for Developers"
  description="Behavior-first Alpine.js patterns you can copy, adapt, and ship."
>
  <main id="main-content" class="mx-auto max-w-7xl space-y-8 px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <article class="prose prose-lg">
      <p class="lead">Behavior-first Alpine.js patterns you can copy, adapt, and ship.</p>

      <p>
        HyperUX is not about repackaging HTML elements and functionality as components. It focuses
        on developer-friendly APIs for behavior-heavy UI patterns you can adapt to your own markup
        and styles.
      </p>

      <time datetime="2026-04-20"> Last updated: 20 April 2026 </time>

      <nav>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/patterns/scroll-spy"
              class="inline-block text-sky-600 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-700"
            >
              Read the Scroll Spy documentation
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <a
              href="/patterns/copy-to-clipboard"
              class="inline-block text-sky-600 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-700"
            >
              Read the Copy to Clipboard documentation
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <a
              href="/patterns/combobox"
              class="inline-block text-sky-600 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-700"
            >
              Read the Combobox documentation
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <a
              href="/patterns/dialog"
              class="inline-block text-sky-600 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-700"
            >
              Read the Dialog documentation
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <a
              href="/patterns/command-palette"
              class="inline-block text-sky-600 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-700"
            >
              Read the Command Palette documentation
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <a
              href="/patterns/dropdown"
              class="inline-block text-sky-600 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-700"
            >
              Read the Dropdown documentation
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <a
              href="/patterns/tabs"
              class="inline-block text-sky-600 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-700"
            >
              Read the Tabs documentation
            </a>
          </li>

          <li>
            <a
              href="/patterns/resizable"
              class="inline-block text-sky-600 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-sky-700"
            >
              Read the Resizable documentation
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
